    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>焊工先生的弹球防御</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讲述了焊工先生，一个热爱弹球的勤劳农民的故事。当外星人入侵开始时，他知道该怎么做——他建立了自己的弹球防御系统来保护他的农场和人类免受侵略者的侵害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/32d13703cf412d4e0af5877d75047866.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=102 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/32d13703cf412d4e0af5877d75047866.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/32d13703cf412d4e0af5877d75047866.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/ec62480954440e74c12809d0854e6d66.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=102 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/ec62480954440e74c12809d0854e6d66.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/ec62480954440e74c12809d0854e6d66.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/6f8b2e84699864402b56700d1bcb5f8f.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=102 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/6f8b2e84699864402b56700d1bcb5f8f.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/6f8b2e84699864402b56700d1bcb5f8f.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/c1c9f8dfdf15e5ed828c4fb80f959c5b.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=102 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/c1c9f8dfdf15e5ed828c4fb80f959c5b.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/c1c9f8dfdf15e5ed828c4fb80f959c5b.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/be78c1c7ed3e0153386a5b93e04a1b91.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=102 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/be78c1c7ed3e0153386a5b93e04a1b91.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/be78c1c7ed3e0153386a5b93e04a1b91.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/b607585abcd324b1dc6e9318ac119380.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=102 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/b607585abcd324b1dc6e9318ac119380.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/b607585abcd324b1dc6e9318ac119380.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >如何玩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要激活陷阱，您需要用球击中它。此外，您还可以使用球直接伤害外星人。连续击中更多的陷阱，球会变得更热，造成更大的伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/3bb2a08b9322ce4cfb37c6377b9fbb27.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/3bb2a08b9322ce4cfb37c6377b9fbb27.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/3bb2a08b9322ce4cfb37c6377b9fbb27.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用动作暂停功能，您可以在即兴的弹球场地内任何地方建造和维护陷阱塔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/4ba3492be9334d93ce68ed7c08a9ac8c.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/4ba3492be9334d93ce68ed7c08a9ac8c.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/4ba3492be9334d93ce68ed7c08a9ac8c.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都有一个中央机制，您可以激活和控制它以释放特殊效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/139d4bfaf375f36e5803886a1dc188d4.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/139d4bfaf375f36e5803886a1dc188d4.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/139d4bfaf375f36e5803886a1dc188d4.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的主要目标是摧毁飞碟母舰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/b575fc41eb36397929ba613fc9e98973.poster.avif?t=1770051061\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/b575fc41eb36397929ba613fc9e98973.webm?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255600/extras/b575fc41eb36397929ba613fc9e98973.mp4?t=1770051061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎战一个曲折险恶的敌人吧。</p>",
